column5: CREATE TABLE "schema_migrations" ("version" varchar NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY)
CREATE TABLE "ar_internal_metadata" ("key" varchar NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY, "value" varchar, "created_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, "updated_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL)

CREATE TABLE "wines" ("id" integer PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, "name" varchar, "properties" text, "price" float, "marketplace" varchar, "note" integer, "wine_type" varchar, "created_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, "updated_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL)

CREATE TABLE "users" ("id" integer PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, "email" varchar DEFAULT '' NOT NULL, "encrypted_password" varchar DEFAULT '' NOT NULL, "reset_password_token" varchar, "reset_password_sent_at" datetime(6), "remember_created_at" datetime(6), "created_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, "updated_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL)

CREATE TABLE "experts" ("id" integer PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, "name" varchar DEFAULT '' NOT NULL, "email" varchar DEFAULT '' NOT NULL, "encrypted_password" varchar DEFAULT '' NOT NULL, "reset_password_token" varchar, "reset_password_sent_at" datetime(6), "remember_created_at" datetime(6), "created_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, "updated_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL)

CREATE TABLE "reviews" ("id" integer PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, "rating" integer, "message" text, "wine_id" integer NOT NULL, "expert_id" integer NOT NULL, "created_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, "updated_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT "fk_rails_95e62ec56c"
FOREIGN KEY ("wine_id")
  REFERENCES "wines" ("id")
, CONSTRAINT "fk_rails_1c8952a0d7"
FOREIGN KEY ("expert_id")
  REFERENCES "experts" ("id")
)

CREATE TABLE "prices" ("id" integer PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, "price" integer NOT NULL, "date" date NOT NULL, "wine_id" integer NOT NULL, "created_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, "updated_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT "fk_rails_5b66690b07"
FOREIGN KEY ("wine_id")
  REFERENCES "wines" ("id")
)

CREATE TABLE "searches" ("id" integer PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, "query" text DEFAULT '' NOT NULL, "expert_id" integer, "user_id" integer, "created_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, "updated_at" datetime(6) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT "fk_rails_632069692a"
FOREIGN KEY ("expert_id")
  REFERENCES "experts" ("id")
, CONSTRAINT "fk_rails_e192b86393"
FOREIGN KEY ("user_id")
  REFERENCES "users" ("id")
)
